                   </content:encoded><category>computing</category><category>swift</category><category>learning</category><category>programming</category><category>swift-programming</category><category>ios-development</category><category>swiftui</category><author>Fatbobman</author></item><item><title>修复 iCloud 同步：使用 initializeCloudKitSchema</title><link>https://fatbobman.com/zh/snippet/resolving-incomplete-icloud-data-sync-in-ios-development-using-initializecloudkitschema/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://fatbobman.com/zh/snippet/resolving-incomplete-icloud-data-sync-in-ios-development-using-initializecloudkitschema/</guid><description>使用 initializeCloudKitSchema 解决 iCloud 同步不完整问题。确保 CloudKit Schema 的完整性，避免 Core Data 和 SwiftData 数据同步失败。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 00:20:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;使用 initializeCloudKitSchema 解决 iCloud 同步不完整问题。确保 CloudKit Schema 的完整性，避免 Core Data 和 SwiftData 数据同步失败。&lt;/p&gt;
