                   </content:encoded><category>computing</category><category>swift</category><category>learning</category><category>programming</category><category>swift-programming</category><category>ios-development</category><category>coredata</category><category>swiftdata</category><author>Fatbobman</author></item><item><title>解决 SwiftUI ScrollView 内容截剪问题</title><link>https://fatbobman.com/zh/snippet/preventing-scrollview-content-clipping-in-swiftui/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://fatbobman.com/zh/snippet/preventing-scrollview-content-clipping-in-swiftui/</guid><description>解决 SwiftUI ScrollView 裁剪问题。通过 scrollClipDisabled 和 Introspect 禁用裁切，实现完整内容显示，避免阴影和效果丢失。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 00:20:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;解决 SwiftUI ScrollView 裁剪问题。通过 scrollClipDisabled 和 Introspect 禁用裁切，实现完整内容显示，避免阴影和效果丢失。&lt;/p&gt;
